+```
+
+### Update Operations (User/Agent Initiated)
+
+```
+User: "Create a new issue for testing"
+
+Claude uses Skill:
+  create_issue(
+    title: "Add tests",
+    description: "...",
+    team_id: "team-123"
+  )
+    ‚Üì
+  LinearAgentClient.createIssue(...)
